name: Square's Obstacles
description:
"Just another Flappy- WAIT!"

THIS GAME IS MADE IN 7 HOURS FOR TRIJAM #206

GAME JAM'S THEME: "Just another copy"

This is a short but VERY challenging game. It starts of as a usual copy of that one popular game, but wait... This game has stages? And that's not all! It's not only one simple obstacle this time!

This game is 100% made by me (Shakur Bakhtali), except for 2 free assets, which are one soundtrack and a font.

Enjoy!
